Package com.example.jenxmout.greyhoundauctions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountActivity
    This is the Account Activity class that, when created, allows the user to log in to an existing account, log out if they are signed in, navigate back to home, or navigate to the SignUpActivity class
    AuctionItems
    This is an Auction Items class that holds all the items that are being auctioned for the event
    BackgroundWorker
    This is an BackgroundWorker class that enables communication between the Android app and the database where the auction information is stored
    BidsActivity
    This is the Bids Activity class that displays the bids placed by the current user for the UI
    EventActivity
    This is the Event Activity class that informs the user about the event
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    FundraiserInfo
    This is the Fundraiser Info class that defines the silent auction event and gives functionality to the countdown clock
    FundraiserInfoTest
    This is a JUnit test class that tests the Fundraiser Info class and it's methods/behaviors
    HighestActivity
    This is the Highest Activity class that displays the items for which the user is the current highest bidder
    Item
    This is a Item class that defines an item to be used for the GreyhoundsAuctions event
    ItemActivity
    This is the Item Activity class that...
    ItemTest
    This is a JUnit test class that tests the Item class and it's methods/behaviors
    MainActivity
    This is the Main Activity class that displays the items up for auction and allows users to search by tags, select items, and access other menu options
    SignUpActivity
    This is the SignUp Activity class that allows a new user to create a GreyhoundAuctions accoount
    User
    This is a User class that defines a GreyhoundsAuctions user and includes methods for that user's behavior
    UserTest
    This is a UserTest class to test the methods of the User class
